{
  "stem": "20218.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That's all I can remember from my childhood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was 13 when one day, we heard on the radio about, about Adolf Hitler with his speeches.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember everybody was concentrated by the radio to listen to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they used to say, we have to pray because I think we're going to-- we're going to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He's going to be after Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was just 13.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "To me, it looked like holiday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My father didn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I didn't have school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My brother didn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Little did I know what a holiday I had because a few-- a few weeks later, Poland was occupied.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when they came to Lodz with the soldiers, they started to make raids on the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They called people to the-- to the-- how to-- how called-- not on the street, but in the-- in the court from the houses, and they selected mostly first of all young people.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They selected this one, that one, just with the finger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The soldiers looked ferocious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I remember my mother hid me in a attic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The worst part of it was that our own neighbors, Polacks, they put a finger on us so we couldn't hide.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But somehow I was hidden, and a lot of people were selected to go with the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They never-- we never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There were incidents which I remember we have-- we had-- what do you call it-- a gate, a gate, a wooden gate in our-- in the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And when they took-- when they-- when they called some people, they had little kids on their arm, little babies.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
